26","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28484,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/29\/itikaf-ramadan-last-ten\/","url_meta":{"origin":32823,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet secludes himself in the last ten nights","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 29, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would retreat to the mosque in the last ten nights of Ramadan. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2025, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1171 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36920,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/08\/shirk-grave-worship\/","url_meta":{"origin":32823,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Origins of idolatry in grave worship, graven images","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Umm Habibah and Umm Salamah mentioned a church they saw in Abyssinia that had graven images in it. They mentioned it to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cVerily,